> Does anyone have good or bad experiences with using these types? 
> There seem to be both blade type and a green knob type.

I have successfully used the green-knob type disconnect for my Sqbk, and also my truck. There are cheap versions out there, so buy a good one. I think the cheap one had a red knob.

The multiple battery connect/isolate devices can be found at RV supply places. I had one in my Vanagon.

Jeff '67 Sqbk
